Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:06.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:12.79,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:27.51,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:44.72,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.26,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:50.26,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:56.50,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:01:01.84,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:07.55,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:11.32,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:34.08,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,The work's cheap and tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-san told me that with a smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:42.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But 4,200 yen a day really was cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:42.42,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}4,200 yen = approx. $36.89 USD
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:47.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I have to wake up at 5:30 AM for cooking duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:51.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I had to clean up after dinner, the work\Nday's actually longer than sixteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:56.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,However, being able to eat three meals\Na day and to sleep on a futon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:02:00.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...made me feel more blessed than anything\Nelse since I've been on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:13.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking duty aside, I've only been getting in\Ntheir way in terms of reconstruction work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:15.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever built a scaffold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... can you get the silguard out and knead it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... but what's a silguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard from many seniors who'd gotten jobs that\Nwhat you learn in school won't help at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go move some rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:36.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never expected it to be this useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, at the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great. It's really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good, young fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Delish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you got Kamekichi-san's approval!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.99,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\fsp-2\fs53\shad0\bord2.3\3c&HAEA7C1&\frz0.001\pos(163,85)\c&HF1F6FA&}really happy-looking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:57.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't get all conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even plane a board!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have a long way to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:08.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about how useless you were when you first joined!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you cooked your own meals all this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:18.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, but I didn't have any money so it was always instant ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, you saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Delish...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I won't just be in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:39.16,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}boku wa ima BEDDO de maruku natte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:39.16,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}I'm now curled up in my bed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:47.83,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}tsumaranai koto kangaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:47.83,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Thinking pointless thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:52.88,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}warui yokan no hitotsu hitotsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:52.88,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Whining like a child
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:54.80,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)\fscx80\fs20\fsp-1\bord0\shad0\frz345.351\c&HF1F4F3&\frx20\fry20\pos(332,65)}Open Until 9pm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:54.80,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)\bord2\be1\shad0\fs20\fscy80\frx8\fry16\c&H83B0EC&\3c&H9DF1F3&\frz346.941\pos(315,115)}Motorcycle Bike
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:54.80,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)\fscx80\fs30\fsp-1\bord0.1\be1\fscx80\fsp6\shad0\frz347.943\c&H73B2B2&\3c&H6FAFB0&\pos(318,225)\frx14\fry24}AJIMA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:04:00.72,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}kodomo mitai ni dada wo konete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:04:00.72,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}About every one of my bad premonitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:04:00.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The new bike that Shin-san picked out for me costs 43,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:06.35,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}mayonaka sugi kimi ni au tame ni
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:06.35,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Past midnight, my legs got tangled up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:06.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Being paid 4,200 yen a day, I'll be able to\Nmake that money in a little over ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:11.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already been here two days, so I have eight more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:14.74,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}motsureta ashi de boku wa tada hashitta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:14.74,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Simply running to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:20.91,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}kimi to nani wo saigo ni hanasu no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:20.91,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}What will I talk about with you in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I started riding my bike, not knowing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:29.21,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}ironna kotoba ga chirakatta mama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:29.21,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}There are so many words just scattered about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was uneasy and in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:35.01,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}tokidoki reizouko no unarigoe ga
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:35.01,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}At times the humming of the fridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:35.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But this place is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:43.43,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}maru de dareka no henji no you ni hibita
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:43.43,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Sounds like somebody's response.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It starts to feel like I've always been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:48.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Being here and working all day long,\Nseeing everyone's happy faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:48.44,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}mayonaka semai rojiura wo nukete
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:48.44,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Running through the narrow back alley in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...made me indescribably happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:56.57,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}hashitta boku wa kage ni oikosareta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:56.57,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}I was overtaken by a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That felt comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:11.54,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}ima kimi no soba de ima kimi no chikaku de
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:11.54,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Now, by your side... Now, somewhere near you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:18.09,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}nani ga kawatte shimatta no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:18.09,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}I wonder what has changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:32.36,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}ima kimi no sono te wa ima kimi no egao wa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:32.36,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}Now, your hands... Now, your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:39.36,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}nani wo motomete iru no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:39.36,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,300)}I wonder what they're longing for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in my hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs42\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\pos(422,366)\c&H158FE1&}Huff Huff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwako-san, it's about Yamada-san that I met the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When will she come here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:10.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll be here again soon, but why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if I could ask her to make me some bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to speak with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:21.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was introduced to us through him, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:28.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him, but Mayama-kun told me that Yamada-san is busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:35.13,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Mayama! He's trying to cover up her existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.59,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, it's to be expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.51,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What should you do, Miwako?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.63,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,The responsibility is enormous... rather!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H0E94E1&\pos(432,377)}"Huh—!? There's 2 Miwako-sans!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miwako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:49.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that I got some really pretty colors to come out.\NI wanted to show them to you, so I brought them over right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:52.85,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the actual person shows up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.73,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,With timing one only finds in a manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:53.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H0E94E1&\pos(432,377)}"{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}Uh oh, Miwako-san's hair—"
