Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H0E94E1&\pos(432,377)}"Uh oh, Miwako-san's hai{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}r—"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H0E94E1&\pos(432,377)}"Uh oh, Miwako-san's hair{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}—"
