Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:55.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\b0\fscx65\fs39\fsp5\3c&HECFCFE&\c&H0E94E1&\pos(432,377)}"Uh oh, Miwako-san's hair—"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Yamada-san is working with Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:11.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what did this Miwako-san say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:19.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"She might be able to give up easier if you just\Nlet her see you and Rika-san together."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Input coming from someone of the same sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like dropping a bomb or a shock therapy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that'll actually have the opposite effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Rika-san doesn't think anything\Nof you when it comes to you as a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:44.45,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\fnTimes New Roman\fscx60\b0\shad2\fs38\4c&HA3A59E&\bord0.01\be1\c&H1F1E1A&\frz9.788\pos(398,189)\frx2\fry354}The Axe\Nof Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:41.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Yamada might think something\Nlike, "Oh, I might still have a chance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Morita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:44.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and put away that axe of truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:46.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:51.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, you should just show it to her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it, to Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:08:05.09,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs88\fnAlsina Ultrajada\bord0.1\be1\fscy80\shad0\move(758,1734,758,486)\c&H4C3092&\3c&H5A5A5A&}Ho\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo\NHo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:08:02.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pathetic self, who is running circles around\NRika-san in an effort to get her attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That would kill even the love of someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:16.48,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say right away, but will you let me ask\Nyou to do jobs for me from time to time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:21.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'd heard from Mayama-kun that you seem busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:31.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Mayama described me to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he ever talks about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:39.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like, "I pity her," or "I hope she can find happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:45.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just delved into some mean-spirited thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama wouldn't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:56.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was Mayama's kindness that led him to lie\Nin order to prevent Rika-san and I from meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:02.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been kind, and I'm sure he'll continue to be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he probably will forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:12.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I really don't know what's going on anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:19.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You often lose track of your own feelings,\Nmuch less someone else's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:24.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually questionable whether Yamada-san still likes you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as that thing with chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:33.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the first person she saw, it feels like she's\Nsticking to you because she thinks you're her parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:39.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, how can I overwrite that impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:45.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you think preciously of Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:50.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it might be Yamada who is growing up to\Nbe a weak person and is feeling stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about yourself, Morita?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu is confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man! I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:23.44,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita, why do you avoid involvement like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not around...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Dinner's served!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurrah, it's chow time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Delish...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, can I have more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:54.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:56.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:01.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me really happy to see other\Npeople enjoying what I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:06.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It really calms me down when it feels like I'm being useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It relieves me of my worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually feel as if I want to stay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, smiling like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:16.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How you have a festival mask smile on your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how long do you intend on staying here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you saved up that 40,000 for a bike already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:35.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun was in a middle of a journey, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,His cooking's so yummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been quick... has it really been ten days already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you looking dazed for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:55.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're, um... in the middle of a soul search, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:59.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it's not like I left to find myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll refill some fresh barley tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:10.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I just randomly... how should I put it....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:13.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply wondered, "How far could I ride?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't seem to find a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:20.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And before that, I didn't even know what I was suited for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.02,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.10,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I couldn't hear it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:34.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On a journey with your bicycle? You must be an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:39.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something only people with lots of free time would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:43.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you can keep eating, even though you're\Nconfused and wandering about, is thanks to your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how old are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Twenty-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty old!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working since I was sixteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It frustrates me just looking at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How you worry and wander!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even have that luxury!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:03.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,0)\3c&H514C6F&\b0\frz-30\fs34\fscy125\shad0\bord1\pos(694,188)\c&H635470&}Squeeze
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H408095&\fnTimes New Roman\b0\shad0\bord0\fscx75\fs24\pos(560,50)\c&H5992B2&}It's too crowded,\Nget out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:03.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H6A98A3&\b0\fs22\fscx80\be1\bord0.1\shad0\move(537,330,523,360)\frz344.988\c&H95A3B8&}Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H4E7FC4&\fs22\bord0.1\be1\shad0\move(478,417,464,446)\frz22.548\c&H6FA3DA&}delinquent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had nine siblings and my family was poor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was kicked out of my house at the age of fifteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you are just spoiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand my—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief. Thanks for your good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you at the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:18.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That you're not allowed to brag about how\Nunfortunate you are, Rokutarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only person with misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:24.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We all hold that in ourselves and work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When we start competing about things\Nlike that, there's just no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're finishing up over in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can send two young guys back over here next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:38.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for working you so hard, Riki-san, Matsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:44.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We ate better food than usual so we had a lot more horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.60,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Box: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Cinnamon-Seasoned Cracknel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:54.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We all know that you've been through hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:14:00.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We also know that you're an idiot, that you talk too much, and\Nthat you're quietly sharpening the planes at night in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takemoto-kun, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've helped us a lot while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:10.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:16.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:21.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were wondering how far you could ride, but you\Nstill haven't found the answer to that yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:31.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just going to be smiling like a ghost, you should\Nride to your heart's content instead of just staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:34.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing like that to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:41.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is whether you did\Nsomething to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:04.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna test your courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Test my courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You can see straight through to the bottom of this bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Elegant, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just make it all the more scary\Nif you keep looking at your footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work well if you just look a little ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you can't look too far ahead either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:28.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, did you ever try to walk across a\Ncrosswalk while stepping only on the white parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:34.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mysterious... even though what we're doing is the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:41.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...just looking down and being scared makes you\Nunable to do what you used to be able to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.34,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\c&H67665B&\fs48\shad0\move(697,327,697,567)\3c&HF5F3EF&\frz8.842}P-Please\Nwait
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:45.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you seem fine, Shin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I've been crossing this bridge since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:57.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't take it here anymore and bolted...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:02.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But walking here makes me somewhat nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like this bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:15.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't forgive myself for having fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I got worked up and crossed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I got used to it, I did it backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end with my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed that you didn't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:30.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't have my book bag on me,\NI wouldn't be standing here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takemoto-kun, want to get your fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:37.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't bring my wallet with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:40.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Rokutarou's saying that he'll buy it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for e-earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that was my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the chief told me to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And... this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:56.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief! ...told me to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:03.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The fortune that I pulled was for a little bit of luck..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:08.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rokutarou laughed and said,\N"That's lame! It fits you perfectly..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:13.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I thought, "Shoot," I also agreed that it fit me perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:21.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge that I crossed on the way back as I drank the\Nnow-warm cola wasn't nearly as scary as it was earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:28.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean... Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:33.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means you're going to Wakkanai... that's far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to see you leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:44.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a parting gift. They're some half-used phone cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:46.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hokkaido can get cold, even in the summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a windbreaker. It's used though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrap this around your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:54.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:59.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, where's Shin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:03.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he left, saying that he's going back\Nhome. He hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:04.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The bicycle shop is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, in that case, I should get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:24.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the hills are really tough when you haven't rode in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:34.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend it to you. It's a little old, but it's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already fixed it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:40.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Shin-san, this is for long-distance biking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why do you have such a bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? Well, y-you see... how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:50.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I also did it when I was in college...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:54.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That going around Japan thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:56.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shin-san, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:58.33,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscx80\fs35\shad0\3c&HB5C9ED&\c&H758FC1&\pos(306,251)\frz7.021}Ah... how\Nembarrassing{\fnArial}—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:58.33,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\3c&H4F4849&\fs52\bord2.5\shad0\pos(544,63)\frz10.468\c&HBD9095&}Crushed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On a self-realization quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:03.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We also found Shin collapsed in the middle of his journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:08.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep. Inside a bamboo forest in\NKyoto where we were working at.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin was adorable back then, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's adorable now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When we saw Takemoto-kun collapsed the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:22.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really thought, "Ah, here comes another\None! A wanderer of adolescence!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:25.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that Shin-san did something so immature—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:30.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, please spend that 50,000 that you\Nsaved to supplement your food budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I put a map in the bicycle's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with some tools and a spare tire tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:41.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're on the road, you won't\Nfind too many shops or residences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be too many places to get water either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So use the stations that you'll find along the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a few along the national road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-san, um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:53.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:56.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to thank me. I'm only lending it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop by again on the way back to return that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be here throughout August.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:03.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:04.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you stop by on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:14.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And please make us a delish meal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, just how long do you intend on chatting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go already, there's no end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, um, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:33.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring back some souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us some crabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:35.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it my best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ride well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:40.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:42.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for trucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:43.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:49.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything! I'm off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:59.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I start riding once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:05.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I've lost the idea that I could\Nfind an answer through riding...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:10.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At least I've started riding again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:14.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
